<i>What if I
couldn't fight no more?</i>

20:49.915 --> 20:52.251
<i>I was just so scared
you guys were gonna hate me.</i>

20:52.251 --> 20:54.545
<i>But I was
just as scared of going back</i>

20:54.545 --> 20:56.672
<i>to the old, fucked up Mike.</i>

20:56.672 --> 20:58.257
<i>The guy who had everyone,
including me,</i>

20:58.257 --> 21:01.093
<i>convinced I was gonna
end up in an early grave.</i>

21:05.097 --> 21:06.515
<i>
Those were my choices.</i>

21:15.024 --> 21:18.152
<i>I could go back
to being Cus's monster.</i>

21:18.152 --> 21:21.405
<i>Don's meal ticket.</i>

21:21.405 --> 21:25.117
<i>Or I could be
the elevated man Ray Ray,</i>

21:25.117 --> 21:27.578
<i>Imam Siddiq,
and Maya saw inside of me...</i>

21:30.247 --> 21:31.499
<i>
That I wanted to be.</i>

21:33.042 --> 21:34.752
<i>
And I had to decide now.</i>
